{"tid":1978795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（圍爐）王毅致電送暖 譚德塞︰歷史自有公斷 總有一天會真相大白","createTime":"2020-04-19T03:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T05:22:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e17665d862037c5bb74a004eeb473bbb1ec70f6c","tid":1978795,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/19/phpsJQC17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F19%2FphpsJQC17.jpg&h=19f98f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在美國川普宣布暫停金援世界衛生組織（WHO），並多次批評世衛秘書長譚德塞引發外界關注，不過中國外交部長王毅昨（18日）親電秘書長譚德塞，強調對譚德塞的大力支持，還承諾會加大對WHO的支持力度。譚德塞也稱，雖然遭受各種攻擊，但他相信總有一天會真相大白。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部表示，王毅昨致電給世衛秘書長譚德塞，表達支持世衛組織跟力挺譚德塞的立場，王毅稱其就任以來致力於全球公共衛生事業，得到各方高度肯定，還大讚譚德塞以高票當選，一直得到會員國高度信任，「作為首個來自發展中國家尤其是非洲大陸的秘書長，也象徵著人類文明的進步發展」。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，相信譚德塞將會帶領世衛組織秉持職業操守和科學態度，繼續協調國際社會共同抗擊疫情，還承諾願在現有合作基礎上，透過多種管道，加大對世衛組織的支持力度。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞則感謝中國對世界衛生組織持續堅定的支持，譚德塞指出，病毒不分國界，國際社會加強團結至關重要。只有團結一致抗疫，人類才能阻止病毒蔓延，若國際社會出現分裂，病毒就會乘虛而入，加速擴散，疫情持續的時間將會更長，並會失去更多生命。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞也稱，雖然他本人和世衛組織受到各種攻擊，但他相信，只要堅持作對的事情，總有一天事實會真相大白，歷史自有公斷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3138526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3138526&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=470e954c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3138526&h=4c229e7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3138526</a>"},{"pid":"749b9b58e180fd71d3659b2d33634e6c2f2a560e","tid":1978795,"uid":110568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅持「作對」的事情"},{"pid":"d9e256b2fba01c35aad3a691cceff617e4c46ef4","tid":1978795,"uid":300785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"王毅：我好支持你ga 我地加你十蚊人工同廿蚊賄賂費好冇？"},{"pid":"fe3178154421a4dc8860d3eb14c31409441df481","tid":1978795,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"真相大白<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200201/1536pix/1580562562_15ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200201%2F1536pix%2F1580562562_15ff.png&h=5aa63b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx9EOLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx9EOLw.jpg&h=18b47f79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70c1007111bfb07e213799aaf6875ae469d4ef8e","tid":1978795,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"對的事情就係幫主子淡化疫情，同埋淡化細箘武器呢個事實，幫主子甩身"},{"pid":"4c9153ce282afc89782ce504a7a19c4f1bdd3432","tid":1978795,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"譚德塞:沒事兒沒事兒<br />\n歷史會還我公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91ec3d88bbcacd7066f35b0ef5834c90d03ab73","tid":1978795,"uid":30476,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"歷史： 又玩9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b8d9e3ff8c668846a08cef101a19183af33016","tid":1978795,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"國際性互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30ef841a603de651860139a9c0877c9a7608ae1","tid":1978795,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"64歷史有公論未？"}]}